{
  "texts": [
    "The models were applied to three languages, including English, German and Arabic.",
    "The authors compare their models to many systems proposed in the research literature.",
    "For English, the models were compared to 4 state-of-the-art systems [35,37,56,80].",
    "Three state-of-the-art systems were compared for German [3,70,147].",
    "For Arabic, the models were compared to the system of Benajiba et al. [19].Halwe et al."
  ]
}